{
  "stem": "4700.2",
  "chunk_idx": 13,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 79,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And they gassed my parents.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 79,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And it took me quite a while to-- to comprehend the whole thing.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 79,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And once we knew it, we lost all hope that we'll see anybody who's gone east.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 80,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And then the typhus came with these people.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 80,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And--",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 81,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "They brought the germs with them.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 82,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "They brought the lice.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 83,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And lots of people died, still after the end of the war.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 83,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And we tried to care for these people.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 83,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But meanwhile, the Germans have taken anything they could take.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 83,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And they sent their families westward.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 83,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And they took-- all the provisions that there were for the camp, they took with them.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 83,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And they took the livestock.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 83,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "They took just anything.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 83,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And there was just nothing in the camp to-- to give those people, to help them survive.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 83,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "[SIGHS]",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 84,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So on the last day of the war, we-- [SIGHS] a group of us, we were working out in the fields.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 84,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And we had glass houses, where we had cucumbers.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 84,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Well, we didn't.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 84,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They had.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 84,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And so we decided we'll go and get the cucumbers, or whatever we can find, any leaves or anything, just so that there is something in the camp.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 85,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And so we were trying to harvest these.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 85,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And on the road, which was next to the garden, the Germans were fleeing.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 85,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "The German columns were fleeing from the north.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 85,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And the Russian pilots came down and bombed the road.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 85,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And then they saw us.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 85,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So they thought it's going to be fun to hit us, too.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 86,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So we were trying to hide.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 86,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But they-- in the glass house.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 86,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But they could see us from-- they shot at us, they-- with the machine guns or whatever.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 86,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So in the end, we thought there's nothing for it.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 86,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "We've got to make a run.",
      "word_count": 6
    }
  ],
